{"tid":1048754,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"每次見到整容怪，我都會刻意起佢面前摸下自己塊面","createTime":"2019-03-05T23:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T04:58:34.000Z","uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12d4dd1e05242577b553d0f2a18c62e996d421b7","tid":1048754,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇得出佢整左邊忽，我就摸自己邊忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次搭𨋢見到有條女整到個鼻好撚怪<br />\n<br />\n我就起佢面前不停檢查自己個鼻<br />\n<br />\n摸下鼻樑，抆下鼻窿<br />\n<br />\n再不地扮偷偷望佢個鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢意識到就dup低頭<br />\n<br />\n到地一開𨋢門就奔走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4034f5ed0ed4b6aacc28847e580c9ed5d99faf3b","tid":1048754,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:25:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9636af3ee3e0271c4ca569077dd08d88663a61d7","tid":1048754,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:27:30.000Z","msg":"下次又試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484baa8baccf6f24011144e9cf0f27a3e5b63f8f","tid":1048754,"uid":110939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:30:02.000Z","msg":"仆街仔，不過我中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1659fcfbaf7b56f0ba2294201ee559832908a32a","tid":1048754,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:31:31.000Z","msg":"之前有個客 已經俾我地話佢整容<br />\n尋日再見到佢 帶曬帽 太陽眼鏡 同口罩<br />\n有個同事同佢熟d 傾下計<br />\n佢塊面瘀左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35beebcafafba88cca8ade892541b5313af7eb24","tid":1048754,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有條友考試出貓攞100分，再起你面前扮勁<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎<br />\n<br />\n對付既方法<br />\n<br />\n就係告比老師知<br />\n<br />\n拆穿佢！拆穿佢！<br />\n<br />\n同理<br />\n<br />\n你整容，咁撚自信做乜？<br />\n<br />\n仲要九成人整容其實整到奇撚怪怪<br />\n<br />\n我要話你知<br />\n<br />\n考試出貓拎高分是不值得炫耀既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5107af4ac0b0137563e563d293b7fbd19561f","tid":1048754,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:44:02.000Z","msg":"整容仲要去大陸整？<br />\n<br />\n花錢整，就不如整勁d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開眼頭開到小丑咁<br />\n<br />\n隆鼻，隆到成條賓州咁<br />\n<br />\n最終，大家都係蛇精咁款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfd7d4369a0ff92145b5d720d2f8858f1700ece","tid":1048754,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"屈Sir未食藥？"},{"pid":"4d5fcaafacbde0797f980f03a9c083e2259fd7d0","tid":1048754,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbfd7d4369a0ff92145b5d720d2f8858f1700ece","tid":1048754,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"屈Sir未食藥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:56:43.000Z","msg":"你整容？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3237e34ca3586f8370b67baf761608ac2a7466","tid":1048754,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}